cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is about object tracking, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a novel method for multi-kernel learning, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve analyzing video data, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO).
